### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">وَلِسُلَيْمَـٰنَ ٱلرِّيحَ عَاصِفَةً تَجْرِى بِأَمْرِهِۦٓ إِلَى ٱلْأَرْضِ ٱلَّتِى بَـٰرَكْنَا فِيهَا ۚ وَكُنَّا بِكُلِّ شَىْءٍ عَـٰلِمِينَ</span>

### English

And to Solomon We subjected the raging winds, blowing by his command to the land We had showered with blessings. It is We Who know everything.